- Tcpdump complements GUI tools like Wireshark, offering command-line precision and efficiency.
- Tcpdump is a powerful tool for capturing, filtering, and displaying packets.
- Alongside Wireshark and Tshark, it is essential for protocol analysis.
- Even at an introductory level, Tcpdump demonstrates its ability to handle large volumes of traffic efficiently.
